    "Apple does not allow the “%@” capability to be modified on this Bundle ID. It may be required, or it might only be changeable on developer.apple.com.": {
      "comment": "A localized string explaining that a specific feature is not changeable on a given bundle ID. The argument is the name of the feature.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apple erlaubt es nicht, die Funktion „%@“ für diese Bundle ID zu ändern. Sie ist möglicherweise erforderlich oder lässt sich nur auf developer.apple.com ändern."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apple no permite modificar la capacidad «%@» en este Bundle ID. Puede ser obligatoria o quizá solo se pueda cambiar en developer.apple.com."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apple n'autorise pas la modification de la capacité « %@ » pour ce Bundle ID. Elle peut être requise ou modifiable uniquement sur developer.apple.com."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apple non consente di modificare la funzionalità “%@” su questo Bundle ID. Potrebbe essere obbligatoria o modificabile solo su developer.apple.com."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apple では、この Bundle ID で「%@」機能を変更できません。必須であるか、developer.apple.com でのみ変更できる場合があります。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apple는 이 Bundle ID에서 “%@” 기능을 수정하는 것을 허용하지 않습니다. 필수 항목이거나 developer.apple.com에서만 변경할 수 있습니다."
          }
        },
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apple staat niet toe dat de mogelijkheid ‘%@’ voor deze Bundle ID wordt gewijzigd. Mogelijk is deze vereist of alleen te wijzigen op developer.apple.com."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A Apple não permite modificar o recurso “%@” neste Bundle ID. Ele pode ser obrigatório ou só pode ser alterado em developer.apple.com."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Apple does not allow this capability to be modified on this Bundle ID. It may be required, or only changeable on developer.apple.com.": {
