    "Automatically distribute new builds for this app to testers in this group. This setting can only be changed in App Store Connect (web) after the group is created.": {
      "comment": "A footer for the \"Enable automatic distribution\" toggle in the \"New Beta Group\" sheet. It explains that this setting can only be changed after the group is created in App Store Connect.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Neue Builds dieser App automatisch an Tester in dieser Gruppe verteilen. Diese Einstellung kann nach dem Erstellen der Gruppe nur in App Store Connect (Web) geändert werden."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Distribuye automáticamente las nuevas compilaciones de esta app a los testers de este grupo. Este ajuste solo se puede cambiar en App Store Connect (web) después de crear el grupo."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Distribuez automatiquement les nouveaux builds de cette app aux testeurs de ce groupe. Ce réglage ne peut être modifié que dans App Store Connect (web) après la création du groupe."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Distribuisci automaticamente le nuove build di questa app ai tester di questo gruppo. Questa impostazione può essere modificata solo in App Store Connect (web) dopo la creazione del gruppo."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "このアプリの新しいビルドをこのグループのテスターに自動的に配信します。この設定は、グループの作成後に App Store Connect（Web）でのみ変更できます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "이 앱의 새 빌드를 이 그룹의 테스터에게 자동으로 배포합니다. 이 설정은 그룹을 만든 후 App Store Connect(웹)에서만 변경할 수 있습니다."
          }
        },
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
