    "Each app receives a message via its topic (bundle ID / package name). Devices must be subscribed to the corresponding topic for delivery.": {
      "comment": "A footer text explaining that each app in the campaign will receive a message, and that devices must be subscribed to the correct topic for it to be delivered.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jede App erhält eine Nachricht über ihr Topic (Bundle ID / Paketname). Geräte müssen das entsprechende Topic abonniert haben, damit die Nachricht zugestellt wird."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cada app recibe un mensaje a través de su topic (Bundle ID / nombre del paquete). Los dispositivos deben estar suscritos al topic correspondiente para que se entregue."
          }
        },
        "es-MX": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": ""
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Chaque app reçoit un message via son topic (Bundle ID / nom du package). Les appareils doivent être abonnés au topic correspondant pour la distribution."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ogni app riceve un messaggio tramite il suo topic (Bundle ID / nome del pacchetto). I dispositivi devono essere iscritti al topic corrispondente per la consegna."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "各アプリは、その topic（Bundle ID / パッケージ名）を介してメッセージを受信します。配信するには、デバイスが対応する topic を購読している必要があります。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "각 앱은 해당 topic(Bundle ID / 패키지 이름)을 통해 메시지를 받습니다. 전달되려면 디바이스가 해당 topic을 구독하고 있어야 합니다."
          }
        },
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Elke app ontvangt een bericht via zijn topic (Bundle ID / pakketnaam). Apparaten moeten geabonneerd zijn op het bijbehorende topic om het bericht te ontvangen."
