    "External testers are invited via email or public link. Up to 10,000 testers. Requires Beta App Review.": {
      "comment": "A footer for the \"Internal Group\" toggle, explaining that external testers need to be invited via email or a public link, and that up to 10,000 testers can be added, but that",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Externe Tester werden per E-Mail oder öffentlichem Link eingeladen. Bis zu 10.000 Tester. Erfordert eine Beta-App-Prüfung."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Los testers externos se invitan por correo electrónico o enlace público. Hasta 10 000 testers. Requiere revisión de la app beta."
          }
        },
        "es-MX": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": ""
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Les testeurs externes sont invités par e-mail ou par lien public. Jusqu’à 10 000 testeurs. Nécessite une vérification de l’app bêta."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "I tester esterni vengono invitati via email o tramite link pubblico. Fino a 10.000 tester. Richiede la revisione dell’app beta."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "外部テスターはメールまたは公開リンクで招待されます。最大10,000人まで。Betaアプリ審査が必要です。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "외부 테스터는 이메일 또는 공개 링크로 초대됩니다. 최대 10,000명. 베타 앱 심사가 필요합니다."
          }
        },
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Externe testers worden uitgenodigd via e-mail of een openbare link. Tot 10.000 testers. Vereist beoordeling van de bèta-app."
